transcripts.text: In the Pilbara, not too far from Karratha, an airport owned by a communist Chinese government-owned company has now been established.  Further down south, 260 kilometres from Perth, a communist Chinese government-owned company has bought the Meriden airport from the Labor government for $1.  China can now fly from the Pilbara to Meriden to Perth.  Did you know any of this?  They try to keep us in the dark.  Protect and defend Australia.  Vote 1, United Australia Party.  Authorised by James Macdonald for the United Australia Party, Brisbane.
